text: Luna I qui inciderit difficile euadetseþe afeallað earfoðlice he ætwint.
Luna II, cito consurgetraþe he arist.
Luna III, non euadethe na ætwint.
Luna IIII, laboret et surgethe swincð & arist.
Luna V, tricabit et surgethe sipað & arist.
Luna VI, non euadethe na ætwint.
Luna VII, medicina sanabiturmic læcedome he bið gehelend.
Luna VIII, diu languet et surgetlange he adlað & arist.
Luna IX, languethe adlað.
Luna X, diu egrotetlange he siclað.
Luna XI, periculo periclitaton fræcnysse he dyrfð.
Luna XII, surgethe arist.
Luna XIII, aliquod tempus egrotatsumne timan he siclað.
Luna XIIII, laborat et surgethe swincð & arist.
Luna XV, periclitathe dyrfð.
Luna XVI, locum mutabit et surgetstowe awent & he arist.
Luna XVII, tricabit et surgethe sipað & arist.
Luna XVIII, laborabit et surgethe swincð & arist.
Luna XIX, similiterealswa.
Luna XX, similiterealswa.
Luna XXI, rem adiuuabitþinc he fultumað.
Luna XXII, languet et surgethe adlað & arist.
Luna XXIII, similiterealswa.
Luna XXIIII, diu languetlange he adlað.
Luna XXV, languet et morieturhe adlað & he swelt.
Luna XXVI, languethe adlað.
Luna XXVII, tricabit et surgethe sipað & arirst.
Luna XXVIII, eger multum iacebit et morieturseoc swiðe he lið & swelt.
Luna XXIX, aeger euadetseoc ætwint.
Luna XXX, eger laborabit et surgetseoc swincð & rist.
